All that running around with my 2 kids.

25
00:05:37,671 --> 00:05:40,048
How are my niece and my nephew anyway?

26
00:05:40,090 --> 00:05:41,884
They are wonderful...

27
00:05:41,925 --> 00:05:44,428
but you know we had
to move in with Madea.

28
