57
00:06:49,868 --> 00:06:52,621
Excuse me. I'm her sister.

58
00:06:52,704 --> 00:06:54,957
She'll be calling you.

59
00:06:58,168 --> 00:06:59,253
Good.

60
00:06:59,336 --> 00:07:01,463
All right, bye.

61
