from child welfare.

191
00:13:23,303 --> 00:13:24,513
Call the next case.

192
00:13:24,555 --> 00:13:26,807
City of Atlanta versus Mabel Simmons.

193
00:13:32,729 --> 00:13:33,856
Madea!

194
00:13:33,897 --> 00:13:36,608
